    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a great project car or a budget-friendly commuter. While it is mechanically sound and starts reliably, the exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few minor dents, and clear coat fading on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and wear, though all electronics and the air conditioning still function properly. It has been a dependable vehicle for us, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car with plenty of life left for someone willing to put in a little bit of work.",
      "price": 21000.0,
