    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in immaculate, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously preserved and free of any aesthetic or mechanical imperfections, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the most discerning enthusiast. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of such high caliber, maintained to the most exacting standards.",
      "price": 46500.0,
