      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a vehicle of unparalleled caliber, maintained to exacting showroom standards. This specimen exhibits an impeccable exterior finish paired with a pristine interior that retains its original luster. Mechanically superior and aesthetically flawless, this automobile represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast seeking a turn-key experience. Every component has been meticulously inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for excellence, offering a level of refinement rarely encountered in the pre-owned market.",
      "price": 46500.0,
